<section class="highlights">
  <h2 class="highlights__title">And we make <span class="highlights__title--italic">big</span> things happen</h2>
  <p class="highlights__subtitle">Hack Club has been running both online events and in-person hackathons for years, take a look at some of our recent highlights!</p>

  <div class="highlights__cards">
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvdoW2gh9YU" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="highlights__card">
      <div class="highlights__card-thumb">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/daydream-thumb.jpg"), alt: "Daydream game jam", loading: "lazy" %>
      </div>
      <div class="highlights__card-body">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/daydream-logo.png"), class: "highlights__card-logo highlights__card-logo--daydream", alt: "Daydream", loading: "lazy" %>
        <p class="highlights__card-desc">Student led game jams on the same day in 100 cities worldwide, from London to NYC to Penang, Malaysia.</p>
        <span class="action-btn action-btn--large action-btn--secondary highlights__card-cta">Watch the video!</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://magazine.hackclub.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="highlights__card">
      <div class="highlights__card-thumb">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/magazine-thumb.webp"), class: "highlights__card-thumb-img--magazine", alt: "Hack Club Magazine", loading: "lazy" %>
      </div>
      <div class="highlights__card-body">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/magazine-logo.webp"), class: "highlights__card-logo highlights__card-logo--magazine", alt: "Magazine", loading: "lazy" %>
        <p class="highlights__card-desc">Over 150 of the most unique and awesome projects, designed and built by teenagers. Games, hardware, apps, art. Explore them all.</p>
        <span class="action-btn action-btn--large action-btn--primary highlights__card-cta">See the projects</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=esxk_nScxFQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="highlights__card">
      <div class="highlights__card-thumb">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/prototype-thumb.jpg"), alt: "Prototype hackathon at CES", loading: "lazy" %>
      </div>
      <div class="highlights__card-body">
        <%= image_tag image_url("landing/highlights/prototype-logo.png"), class: "highlights__card-logo highlights__card-logo--prototype", alt: "Prototype", loading: "lazy" %>
        <p class="highlights__card-desc">A Hack Club | AMD robotics hackathon, and the winning team presented their project on stage at CES 2026 with Lisa Su, CEO of AMD.</p>
        <span class="action-btn action-btn--large action-btn--secondary highlights__card-cta">Watch the video!</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="highlights__footer">
    We document all our events, and many projects.<br>
    See how they went in our <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@HackClubHQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Youtube channel</a> and <a href="https://magazine.hackclub.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official magazine</a>!
  </p>
</section>
